00:52:23.320 --> 00:52:26.870
You don't even know what's ahead. do you?

561
00:52:27.410 --> 00:52:31.040
Well...but because the situation is different

562
00:52:31.160 --> 00:52:32.620
I am also not certain

563
00:52:42.050 --> 00:52:43.970
Huh? Can't be

564
00:52:44.220 --> 00:52:45.090
what happened?

565
00:52:46.220 --> 00:52:48.430
It's Shota! he is alive!

566
00:52:48.550 --> 00:52:50.140
Ah. don't answer the phone...

567
00:52:50.260 --> 00:52:52.020
Hey? Shota? Is it Shota?

568
00:52:59.520 --> 00:53:01.150
What happened to Daisuke?

569
00:53:01.280 --> 00:53:03.820
I don't know…

570
00:53:12.950 --> 00:53:13.660
Shota!

571
00:53:13.790 --> 00:53:15.160
How is this going?

572
00:53:15.290 --> 00:53:16.540
Really

573
00:53:19.080 --> 00:53:20.170
OK let's go

574
00:53:20.540 --> 00:53:22.670
Wait. why are you so calm?

575
00:53:28.550 --> 00:53:29.390
Huh?

576
00:53:38.980 --> 00:53:41.900
Um. can you hurry up if you want to come?

577
00:53:42.020 --> 00:53:43.690
Next we have to run

578
00:53:43.820 --> 00:53:45.740
In the end. the guy still came

579
00:53:45.860 --> 00:53:47.570
Why do you seem to be more drunk than before?

580
00:53:50.160 --> 00:53:52.120
He must have had that drink

581
00:53:53.740 --> 00:53:55.370
I messed up

582
00:54:05.840 --> 00:54:07.010
This is…

583
00:54:07.840 --> 00:54:09.010
This taiko...

584
00:54:09.340 --> 00:54:10.550
Hurry up. run!

585
00:54:11.050 --> 00:54:13.430
That is the sound of some festival...

586
00:54:13.560 --> 00:54:14.850
Stop talking about this!

587
00:54:14.970 --> 00:54:16.680
Can't wait any longer. let's go!

588
00:54:16.810 --> 00:54:17.310
But…

589
00:54:17.430 --> 00:54:19.390
You didn't see it with your own eyes. that's why you said that

590
00:54:19.520 --> 00:54:20.980
Daisuke. let's go

591
00:54:23.020 --> 00:54:24.110
Let's go

592
00:54:24.480 --> 00:54:26.360
So... what will happen to that person?

593
00:54:26.490 --> 00:54:27.990
this...

594
00:54:30.240 --> 00:54:33.330
My mother always said not to go against your conscience

595
00:54:34.830 --> 00:54:35.950
Sir!

596
00:54:36.080 --> 00:54:38.120
-Wait...
-Hurry up

597
00:54:38.830 --> 00:54:40.370
-Come here
-Wait

598
00:54:40.790 --> 00:54:42.540
Even if you tell me to hurry up...

599
00:54:42.670 --> 00:54:43.840
Hurry up

600
00:54:52.220 --> 00:54:53.430
Are you OK?

601
00:54:58.890 --> 00:55:01.060
This... how is this?

602
00:55:07.320 --> 00:55:08.740
Are you OK?

603
00:55:10.070 --> 00:55:11.610
Ah...much more comfortable

604
00:55:12.820 --> 00:55:14.280
Let's go

605
00:55:14.410 --> 00:55:15.200
Start running

606
00:55:15.330 --> 00:55:17.700
-Come on
-No way I just vomited

607
00:55:25.500 --> 00:55:30.090
How has it been since just now? What are you kidding?

608
00:55:33.760 --> 00:55:34.930
It's coming

609
00:55:36.010 --> 00:55:37.560
Hey!

610
00:55:38.020 --> 00:55:42.060
It's too dangerous to walk on the rails!

611
00:55:44.980 --> 00:55:46.900
-What happened?
-Someone...

612
00:55:48.190 --> 00:55:50.110
Hey!

613
00:55:50.240 --> 00:55:52.280
It's too dangerous to walk on the rails!

614
00:55:52.400 --> 00:55:53.410
Run!

615
00:55:54.070 --> 00:55:55.200
Never mind. run!

616
00:55:55.320 --> 00:55:57.580
Why? Can you ask him to help us?

617
00:55:57.700 --> 00:55:58.450
Please run!

618
00:55:58.580 --> 00:56:01.120
Don't push me. I told you not to push!

619
00:56:02.500 --> 00:56:04.330
Hey…

620
00:56:04.880 --> 00:56:10.260
-It's too dangerous to walk on the rails!
-What... how... what the hell!

621
00:56:11.420 --> 00:56:12.550
What happened?

622
00:56:15.260 --> 00:56:17.430
Run... hurry up! Run!

623
00:56:18.310 --> 00:56:19.390
Run away!

624
00:56:28.150 --> 00:56:28.940
Miki...

625
00:56:29.070 --> 00:56:30.110
Shota?

626
00:56:31.360 --> 00:56:34.450
What are you doing? The old man is coming!

627
00:56:39.200 --> 00:56:39.910
You are killing him!

628
00:56:40.040 --> 00:56:41.950
This monster is not your boyfriend

629
00:56:46.330 --> 00:56:47.380
Shota?

630
00:56:51.130 --> 00:56:52.170
Let's go

631
00:57:01.390 --> 00:57:04.810
Could she be... some hero?

632
00:57:06.190 --> 00:57:09.400
Luckily it's not me

633
00:57:29.590 --> 00:57:32.170
Isakinu Tunnel?

634
00:57:45.390 --> 00:57:46.690
Want to go in?

635
00:58:50.460 --> 00:58:54.710
Is there something wrong with this weird place?

636
00:58:55.210 --> 00:58:58.670
No. actually something happened here too

637
00:58:58.800 --> 00:59:01.300
Due to infighting

638
00:59:01.590 --> 00:59:03.850
Internal fighting at such a time?

639
00:59:03.970 --> 00:59:05.600
That's too bad

640
00:59:08.770 --> 00:59:11.980
I hate that kind of person the most

641
00:59:12.980 --> 00:59:14.150
That's it

642
00:59:18.690 --> 00:59:19.860
Miss Tsutsumi

643
00:59:21.860 --> 00:59:25.160
Thank you. without you...

644
00:59:25.280 --> 00:59:28.540
No. I just happen to have relevant knowledge

645
00:59:29.250 --> 00:59:33.710
You could have gotten out of trouble alone

646
00:59:36.340 --> 00:59:40.170
After all. I have heard the story. but I still can't help it...

647
00:59:40.590 --> 00:59:41.720
Story?

648
00:59:43.640 --> 00:59:46.680
Anyway. someone is waiting for you

649
00:59:49.020 --> 00:59:50.180
So...

650
00:59:51.350 --> 00:59:53.350
We must return to the real world

651
00:59:55.440 --> 00:59:56.400
OK

652
01:00:12.370 --> 01:00:13.790
Hey look

653
01:00:14.630 --> 01:00:15.750
It's an exit!

654
01:00:16.290 --> 01:00:17.880
Ray of hope...

655
01:00:24.180 --> 01:00:25.590
Let's go

656
01:00:44.570 --> 01:00:47.870
God. it's so bright! Are we saved?

657
01:00:48.240 --> 01:00:51.410
Now you can go home...

658
01:00:59.750 --> 01:01:01.170
So bright

659
01:01:05.880 --> 01:01:07.010
What's wrong?

660
01:01:08.510 --> 01:01:10.560
Nothing. let's go

661
01:01:15.020 --> 01:01:16.270
So bright!

662
01:01:26.740 --> 01:01:27.870
Coming

663
01:01:37.170 --> 01:01:39.330
Wait. there is a car! Hello. there is a car!

664
01:01:42.710 --> 01:01:44.260
Are you all right?

665
01:01:45.510 --> 01:01:48.550
Excuse me. can you drive us?

666
01:01:48.680 --> 01:01:50.600
No problem

667
01:01:58.900 --> 01:01:59.900
Excuse me

668
01:02:00.360 --> 01:02:01.900
Having said that. where is it?

669
01:02:02.020 --> 01:02:02.900
this is Hina

670
01:02:03.030 --> 01:02:04.360
Hina?

671
01:02:05.030 --> 01:02:07.070
Anyway. I'll drive you to the nearest station first

672
01:02:07.200 --> 01:02:08.910
That would be great

673
01:02:09.490 --> 01:02:10.990
But sorry

674
01:02:11.950 --> 01:02:14.080
You are a bit too many...

675
01:02:14.790 --> 01:02:16.540
There is one person who can't go along

676
01:02:17.000 --> 01:02:18.920
It's OK if everyone squeezes

677
01:02:19.040 --> 01:02:22.500
Please spare me. the police will charge me if they catch me

678
01:02:22.630 --> 01:02:23.500
But…

679
01:02:26.670 --> 01:02:27.800
Then I...

680
01:02:27.930 --> 01:02:29.300
I will stay

681
01:02:30.590 --> 01:02:32.760
Everyone get in the car!

682
01:02:33.260 --> 01:02:36.430
No... I don't want Daisuke to not go!

683
01:02:36.454 --> 01:02:38.076
Miki

684
01:02:38.100 --> 01:02:39.940
Please take us all

685
01:02:40.060 --> 01:02:41.480
I just said no

686
01:02:41.610 --> 01:02:43.270
Then i can go to the trunk

687
01:02:43.400 --> 01:02:45.070
It's not like if you don't get caught. you'll be fine.

688
01:02:45.190 --> 01:02:49.490
Well. I want to make sure first

689
01:02:50.410 --> 01:02:53.200
Can any of us drive?

690
01:02:55.160 --> 01:02:57.200
I will

691
01:02:57.750 --> 01:02:58.830
Very good

692
01:02:59.580 --> 01:03:00.620
Get in the car!

693
01:03:00.750 --> 01:03:02.290
Just say no!

694
01:03:04.460 --> 01:03:05.250
You kill?

695
01:03:05.380 --> 01:03:06.880
ok let's go

696
01:03:07.010 --> 01:03:08.720
But…

697
01:03:09.680 --> 01:03:12.680
Don't get me wrong. this guy is also the same

698
01:03:13.140 --> 01:03:14.010
How come…

699
01:03:14.140 --> 01:03:15.220
Wait. no!

700
01:03:15.350 --> 01:03:17.560
This guy is really that!

701
01:03:19.890 --> 01:03:23.360
Anyway. get in the car. hurry up

702
01:03:23.480 --> 01:03:27.440
Get in the car. please drive fast. leave it alone!

703
01:04:01.390 --> 01:04:04.020
Believe me. that guy is really bad

704
01:04:07.020 --> 01:04:08.070
Hey

705
01:04:09.480 --> 01:04:11.780
We've been driving for a long time. is this the right way?

706
01:04:12.860 --> 01:04:16.070
Probably. someone said go straight

707
01:04:16.330 --> 01:04:18.620
Then what's ahead?

708
01:04:19.080 --> 01:04:21.370
There seems to be a shrine

709
01:04:21.500 --> 01:04:23.620
There's a door that glows

710
01:04:23.750 --> 01:04:25.880
It seems that I can return to the real world

711
01:04:26.710 --> 01:04:28.300
The real world...

712
01:04:48.820 --> 01:04:50.610
Huh? It's that guy

713
01:04:51.190 --> 01:04:53.070
Drive fast. fast!

714
01:04:54.860 --> 01:04:56.450
Damn. I can't move!

715
01:04:58.620 --> 01:04:59.740
Hurry up!

716
01:05:03.000 --> 01:05:04.080
Run everyone

717
01:05:04.210 --> 01:05:05.710
Wait a moment!

718
01:05:05.830 --> 01:05:08.750
Wait a moment!

719
01:05:18.850 --> 01:05:21.140
Stupid!

720
01:06:32.250 --> 01:06:33.590
Run away!

721
01:06:46.480 --> 01:06:47.850
That is…

722
01:06:48.140 --> 01:06:50.650
Is someone there to help us?

723
01:06:51.020 --> 01:06:52.940
Miss Tsutsumi. is that house...?

724
01:06:54.230 --> 01:06:57.440
I don't know. I haven't heard of that

725
01:06:57.990 --> 01:06:59.910
Let's go

726
01:07:00.780 --> 01:07:01.870
Wait

727
01:07:02.620 --> 01:07:03.830
What should we do?

728
01:07:05.290 --> 01:07:08.540
Let's go. maybe there's something that can be used as a weapon

729
01:08:04.300 --> 01:08:06.680
I'll go to the second floor to have a look

730
01:08:26.990 --> 01:08:27.990
Daisuke?

731
01:08:28.870 --> 01:08:29.990
Shota!

732
01:08:30.870 --> 01:08:32.210
Miki. wait!

733
01:08:32.330 --> 01:08:33.120
Shota

734
01:08:33.250 --> 01:08:34.710
It's too late

735
01:08:38.500 --> 01:08:39.590
Miki!

736
01:08:41.840 --> 01:08:42.880
Let's go

737
01:09:35.020 --> 01:09:37.600
That is the exit door

738
01:09:37.900 --> 01:09:39.110
Really?

739
01:09:40.860 --> 01:09:43.030
What happened? Let's go over there!

740
01:09:44.900 --> 01:09:48.200
If it wasn't for that student

741
01:09:48.320 --> 01:09:50.580
I would have been the one 
who walked into the light first

742
01:10:04.300 --> 01:10:06.090
Miss Tsutsumi. run...

743
01:10:09.140 --> 01:10:11.560
If I walked into that light first...

744
01:10:17.020 --> 01:10:19.690
Maybe she would be the one rescued

745
01:10:21.980 --> 01:10:23.400
Hurry up!

746
01:10:26.240 --> 01:10:27.150
Let's go...

747
01:10:32.870 --> 01:10:35.250
Teacher!

748
01:10:51.350 --> 01:10:53.600
I'll stop him. you go first

749
01:11:07.820 --> 01:11:10.860
You better go first. leave this to me!

750
01:11:11.160 --> 01:11:14.490
You better go first. leave this to me

751
01:11:14.830 --> 01:11:15.830
But…

752
01:11:15.950 --> 01:11:17.450
Never mind. let's go!

753
01:11:17.910 --> 01:11:20.000
In that case Miss Tsutsumi...

754
01:11:20.960 --> 01:11:23.960
I'll go right away. you hurry up!

755
01:11:24.460 --> 01:11:27.380
I'll go right away. you hurry up!

756
01:11:53.620 --> 01:11:56.700
Teacher! Teacher!

757
01:12:04.210 --> 01:12:06.380
Miss Tsutsumi. hurry up!

758
01:12:09.880 --> 01:12:10.920
Hurry up!

759
01:12:11.800 --> 01:12:13.260
What happened?

760
01:12:18.520 --> 01:12:21.350
Miss Tsutsumi. hurry up. hurry up!

761
01:12:30.740 --> 01:12:32.240
Why?

762
01:12:34.320 --> 01:12:35.870
Why?

763
01:12:39.790 --> 01:12:42.120
Why?

764
01:12:43.710 --> 01:12:45.880
Why?

765
01:13:46.270 --> 01:13:48.770
You at that time

766
01:13:49.150 --> 01:13:51.400
I was worried about you about getting hurt

767
01:13:51.530 --> 01:13:54.530
So you told me to go first

768
01:13:57.200 --> 01:13:58.740
So I…

769
01:13:59.950 --> 01:14:03.700
Passed through the glowing door before you

770
01:14:04.830 --> 01:14:07.250
Just like you now

771
01:14:09.880 --> 01:14:11.040
That…

772
01:14:13.670 --> 01:14:15.470
May I ask who are you?

773
01:14:18.180 --> 01:14:22.350
Right. we'll I figured it out later

774
01:14:23.350 --> 01:14:25.560
Able to return to the real world

775
01:14:26.560 --> 01:14:30.650
Only the person who first passed through the door

776
01:14:39.620 --> 01:14:41.030
Welcome back

777
01:15:10.020 --> 01:15:11.520
{\an8}(Thank you)

778
01:15:12.480 --> 01:15:16.480
{\an8}(You have come in handy)

779
01:16:02.000 --> 01:16:07.000
